# Character Abilities
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Track|TYPE:General|DESC:To find tracks or to follow them for 1 mile requires a successful Survival check. You must make another Survival check every time the tracks become difficult to follow.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Plant Wild Shape|TYPE:Wild.Epic.EpicDruid|DESC:You can use your normal wild shape ability to take the form of a plant. The size limitation is the same as your limitation on animal size.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Natural Spell|TYPE:General|DESC:You can complete the verbal and somatic components of spells while in a wild shape. You can also use any material components or focuses you possess, even if such items are melded within your current form.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Leadership|TYPE:General|DESC:Benefits&colon; Having this feat enables you to attract loyal companions and devoted followers, subordinates who assist you.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Improved Initiative|TYPE:General.Fighter|DESC:You get a +4 bonus on initiative checks.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Gargantuan Wild Shape|TYPE:Wild.Epic.EpicDruid|DESC:You can use your wild shape to take the shape of a Gargantuan animal.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Colossal Wild Shape|TYPE:Wild.Epic.EpicDruid|DESC:You can use your wild shape to take the shape of a Colossal animal.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Epic Spellcasting|TYPE:Epic.EpicCleric.EpicDruid.EpicSorcerer.EpicWizard.EpicEldritchKnight.EpicLoremaster.EpicMysticTheurge.CosmicDescryer.HighProselytizer.EpicCerebremancer|DESC:You may develop and cast epic spells. If you are an arcane spellcaster, you may cast a number of epic spells per day equal to your ranks in Knowledge (arcana) divided by 10. If you are a divine spellcaster, you may cast a number of epic spells per day equal to your ranks in Knowledge (religion) or Knowledge (nature) divided by 10.
